he proto-solar abundances prevent us from making a robust comparison between\nthe local and the intra-cluster chemical enrichments. We also note that,\ninterestingly, and despite the large net exposure time (~4.5 Ms) of our\ndataset, no line emission feature is seen around ~3.5 keV.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 3 Jun 2016 16:17:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 18 Aug 2016 09:43:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-24"}
