to alter the complexity of the\nphysiological recordings. To sum up, MDE and RCMDE are expected to be useful\nfor the analysis of physiological signals thanks to their ability to\ndistinguish different types of dynamics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 4 Jun 2016 13:54:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 8 Jul 2016 15:34:44 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 3 May 2017 16:28:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-05-04"}
